      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This protocol provides a blueprint for a configuration state object, which encompasses a trait collection along with all of the common states that affect a view’s appearance. A configuration state encapsulates the inputs that configure a view for any possible state or combination of states. You use a configuration state with background and content configurations to obtain the default appearance for a specific state.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Typically, you don’t create a configuration state yourself. To obtain a configuration state, override the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UICollectionViewCell/updateConfiguration(using:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method in your view subclass and use the state parameter. Outside of this method, you can get a view’s configuration state by using its ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UICollectionViewCell/configurationState-4u37h",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIViewConfigurationState-swift.struct",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UICellConfigurationState-swift.struct",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
